ACCESSORY.name: Mulching Kit for 42-inch Cutting Decks
ACCESSORY.longDescription:
• Mulching Kit for Cub Cadet and Battery Lawn Tractors and Zero-Turn Mowers with 42-inch cutting decks
  • Includes one molded plug and mounting hardware.
  • Ideal for finely cutting grass clippings and redistributing them back into your lawn, providing essential nutrients.
  • Compatible with Troy-Bilt® Super Bronco™ 42E XP and Mustang™ Z42E XP

ACCESSORY.name: Lawn Striping Kit for 42-, 50- and 54-inch Decks
ACCESSORY.longDescription:
Increase your property's curb appeal with a striping kit. Adding patterns to your lawn gives it a professional, well-manicured look. You can mow and stripe at the same time, making it easy to get the lawn you’ve always wanted.

  • Fits Cub Cadet Ultima Series™ Zero Turn Mowers with 42-, 50- and 54-inch Stamped Steel Decks (2019- )
  • Fits Troy-Bilt Mustang Z42 Zero-Turn Riders with 42-, 50- and 54-inch Stamped Steel Decks (2019- )
  • Easy Installation

name: Mustang™ Z42E XP Battery-Powered Zero-Turn Mower
longDescription:
Enjoy listening to playlists, not engine noise, with the battery-powered Troy-Bilt® Mustang™ Z42E XP engineered for noise reduction up to 75% quieter than gas^. Dual electric brushless motors allow mowing up to 3.5 acres of grass or up to 1.5 hours of runtime per charge**. A convenient deck lift foot pedal quickly raises the 42" deck to help mow over roots or clear thresholds. A 3-year limited warranty covers the batteries, while the frame has a limited lifetime warranty.

Documents and Guides
  • Assembly Instructions
  • Calibration Guide

values.value: *Maximum initial battery voltage (measured without a workload) is 56 volts. Nominal voltage is 50.4 volts.
ANSI certified, UL compliant battery and charger
^ vs. Troy-Bilt Mustang Z42 17ARFACSA66 gas mower, measurements taken from the operator position in a lab environment.
